h4. Steps to Reproduce:
# Go to General Configuration
# Set the Base URL using IPv6 address(eg. http://[fe80::e2db:55ff:fed6:832d]:8080).

h4. Expected Result:
Base URL set correctly.

h4. Actual Result:
JIRA returns the following error:
{code}
You must set a valid base URL.
{code}

h4. Suggestion
There is no clear indication of whether JIRA supports IPV6. If it is currently unsupported, it should inform the user while setting the Base Url with a message such as:
{code}
JIRA does not currently support IPV6, please insert a valid IPV4 address.
{code}

